{
    "title": "Depois melhora",
    "artist": "Luiz Tatit",
    "composer": "Luiz Tatit",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span> \n        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>\n\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Verso]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(11)\">D7(11)</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G4/B\">G4/B</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9\">F6/9</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9\">Em9</span>                              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cadd(b5)\">Cadd(b5)</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sempre que alguém daqui vai embora</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(11)\">D7(11)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dói bastante mas depois melhora e com o tempo</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G4/B\">G4/B</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9\">F6/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vira um sentimento que nem sempre aflora mas que fica na memória</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9\">Em9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Depois vira um sofrimento que corrói tudo por dentro</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C(b5)\">C(b5)</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que penetra no organismo, que devora, mas depois também melhora</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sempre que alguém daqui vai embora</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(11)\">D7(11)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dói bastante mas depois melhora e com o tempo</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G4/B\">G4/B</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9\">F6/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Torna-se um tormento que castiga e deteriora feito ave predatória</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9\">Em9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Depois vira um instrumento de martírio duro e lento</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C(b5)\">C(b5)</span>                                          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Uma queda no abismo que apavora, mas depois também melhora</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Ponte]</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#11/13\">A#11/13</span>         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm11#5\">Cm11#5</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7#5\">D7#5</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#7/G\">D#7/G</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>          <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9#5/G\">Em9#5/G</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M/F#\">G7M/F#</span>        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9/E\">Am9/E</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>            <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>\n\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>\n\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#11/13\">A#11/13</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E vira então uma força inexplicável</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm11#5\">Cm11#5</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7#5\">D7#5</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que deixa todo mundo mais amável</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#7/G\">D#7/G</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é conseqüência da saudade</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é que voltou a felicidade</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é que também já era hora</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9#5/G\">Em9#5/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é pra ninguém mais ir embora</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M/F#\">G7M/F#</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9/E\">Am9/E</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vira uma esperança, cresce de um jeito que a gente até balança</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>      \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Às vezes dói bastante mas melhora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim, é só felicidade aqui e agora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É bom, é bom não falar muito que piora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim, é só felicidade</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Sempre que alguém daqui vai embora</span>\n                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7(11)\">D7(11)</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Dói bastante mas depois melhora e com o tempo</span>\n                  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G4/B\">G4/B</span>                        <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6/9\">F6/9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vira um sentimento que nem sempre aflora mas que fica na memória</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9\">Em9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Depois vira um sofrimento que corrói tudo por dentro</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C(b5)\">C(b5)</span>                                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que penetra no organismo, que devora, mas depois também melhora</span>\n\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">[Ponte]</span>\n\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#11/13\">A#11/13</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E vira então uma força inexplicável</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Cm11#5\">Cm11#5</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D7#5\">D7#5</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Que deixa todo mundo mais amável</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#7/G\">D#7/G</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é conseqüência da saudade</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é que voltou a felicidade</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"A#9/F\">A#9/F</span>  \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é que também já era hora</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#6/11\">D#6/11</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em9#5/G\">Em9#5/G</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Um pouco é pra ninguém mais ir embora</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G7M/F#\">G7M/F#</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am9/E\">Am9/E</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span> \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Vira uma esperança, cresce de um jeito que a gente até balança</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>      \n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim</span>\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Às vezes dói bastante mas melhora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim, é só felicidade aqui e agora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>                      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Em11\">Em11</span>    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"Am6\">Am6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É bom, é bom não falar muito que piora</span>\n  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G6\">G6</span>     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F6\">F6</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Enfim, é só felicidade</span>\n",
